snippet.textDisplay:
You can’t see this now because of heartache and emotional pain blocks us from seeing things clearly when tragedy strikes us. If it was meant to be, it will be no matter how rocky the road is that u travel. And sometimes you have to take a detour to actually get where you want to go. And every goodbye opens up a new opportunity to say hello. Don’t stop don’t breakdown keep traveling the path your on and you will be stronger for it when you finally reach your destination. Every door that closes is a opportunity to open a new one and find new friends and new adventures. sometimes we all need a break from each other. A chance to step back, breathe and spend a little time with ourselves to understand the things we don’t have control over. Heartbreak is fleeting. And unfortunately nothing last forever.
Not a fan of you. Just another human being who has experienced heartache and understands how you feel now. But today’s heartache turns into yesterday’s memories and makes you a little stronger tomorrow for having to suffer through it now.
